This will not be displayed in the Draft Issue form Draft when the task is approved Pending Internal Review when issue is sent for internal review Internal Review Completed when internal review is completed Pending Auditee Review when issue is sent for external review Auditee Review Completed when external review is completed Pending Lead Auditor Review when the internal external review form is sent back to the Lead Auditor for review Draft Report Pending Auditee Review when issue is sent for external review in the draft report Draft Report Pending Internal Review when issue is sent for internal review in the draft report Draft Report Request Clarification - When the Approver Requests for clarification in the Draft Audit Report Draft Report Pending Approval - when the draft report is sent for approval. Approved- When the draft report is approved by the approver. Pending Management Support Review - When the issues are sent to management support. Request Clarification - When the management support requests for clarification Report Issued when issue is included as part of report and the report is issued
